Frank Jonasson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frank_Jonasson 0 Frank Jonasson (December 14, 1878 – October 17, 1942) was an American film actor of the silent era. He appeared in 75 films between 1914 and 1930. He was born in Salt Lake City, Utah, and died in Rancho Los Amigos, California.
